OL,3,CMore than 200 arrested at protest
OL,4,Cagainst Palestine Action ban in London
OL,6,FPolice have arrested over 200 people
OL,7,Fduring a mass protest against the ban
OL,8,Fon Palestine Action in central London.
OL,10,FThe Metropolitan Police confirmed all
OL,11,F212 of the arrests made during the
OL,12,Fdemonstration at Trafalgar Square are
OL,13,Ffor showing support for a proscribed
OL,14,Forganisation.
OL,16,FThe ages of those arrested range from
OL,17,F27 years old to 82 years old, the
OL,18,Fforce said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
