OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776168669
OL,3,CMore than 200 arrested at protest
OL,4,Cagainst Palestine Action ban in London
OL,6,FIn a post on X, the Metropolitan
OL,7,FPolice added their officers are
OL,8,F"continuing to make more arrests and a
OL,9,Fgroup remains in Trafalgar Square."
OL,11,FHundreds of protesters gathered in
OL,12,FTrafalgar Square on Saturday afternoon
OL,13,Fwith signs reading "I oppose genocide.
OL,14,FI support Palestine Action".
OL,16,FMany of the mostly elderly
OL,17,Fdemonstrators sat on camping chairs
OL,18,Fand on the ground as they held up
OL,19,Ftheir placards.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@cO]uD@TOUvD@[O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
