OL,3,CMore than 200 arrested at protest
OL,4,Cagainst Palestine Action ban in London
OL,6,FAt the top of the square, near the
OL,7,FNational Gallery, large banners were
OL,8,Fdisplayed reading "Jurors deserve to
OL,9,Fhear the whole truth" and "Israel
OL,10,Fstarves kids".
OL,12,FAmong the demonstrators, Massive
OL,13,FAttack musician Robert Del Naja sat
OL,14,Fwith an "I Support Palestine Action"
OL,15,Fsign despite the consequences a
OL,16,Fpotential arrest could have on his
OL,17,Fmusic career.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@UO]qD@[OUrD@MO]vD@IOUvD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
