OL,3,CMore than 200 arrested at protest
OL,4,Cagainst Palestine Action ban in London
OL,6,FHe said: "Being a musician, obviously,
OL,7,Fthere was a lot of trepidation around
OL,8,Fhow we might not be able to travel and
OL,9,Fget visas.
OL,11,F"But I thought 'this is ridiculous'
OL,12,Fand then the police making that U-turn
OL,13,Fto arrest people again, I thought that
OL,14,Fis even more ridiculous.
OL,16,F"So I'm going to hold a sign today.
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
