OL,3,CMore than 200 arrested at protest
OL,4,Cagainst Palestine Action ban in London
OL,6,F"If I get arrested, I feel very
OL,7,Fconfident that if I stand up in court
OL,8,Fwith the right guidance and say 'this
OL,9,Fwas an unlawful arrest and, therefore,
OL,10,FI don't accept it'."
OL,12,FSeveral individuals, including a man
OL,13,Fand a woman with grey hair, were
OL,14,Fcarried off by officers away from the
OL,15,Fdemonstration.
OL,17,FPolice officers could be seen carrying
OL,18,Fa lady from the protest as people
OL,19,Fchanted "shame on you".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TO]{D@IOU{D@VO]
