OL,3,CMore than 200 arrested at protest
OL,4,Cagainst Palestine Action ban in London
OL,6,FPolice then lifted a man out in
OL,7,Fhandcuffs and walked an elderly
OL,8,Fprotester with a walking stick to the
OL,9,Fpolice vans.
OL,11,FProtest group Defend Our Juries said
OL,12,Fthe demonstration, called Everyone
OL,13,FDay, would show the "resistance" to
OL,14,Fthe ban on Palestine Action is
OL,15,F"stronger than ever".
OL,17,FThe Metropolitan Police said
OL,18,FSaturday's action "is likely to
OL,19,Finvolve offending rather than a lawful
OL,20,Fprotest".
OL,26,@uD@UOUuD@`O]wD@AOUwD@TO]zD@SOU|D@HO]
