OL,3,CMore than 200 arrested at protest
OL,4,Cagainst Palestine Action ban in London
OL,6,FIn March, the force said officers
OL,7,Fwould resume arresting suspected
OL,8,FPalestine Action supporters, as a High
OL,9,FCourt battle over the ban on the group
OL,10,Fcontinues.
OL,12,FThe police paused the arrest of
OL,13,Fdemonstrators in February after the
OL,14,FHigh Court ruled the Government's ban
OL,15,Fwas unlawful, but then decided to
OL,16,Fresume as an appeal against the ruling
OL,17,Fis likely to take several months.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
